  vulnerable versions.

*refbase-0.9.0 (12 Feb 2008)

  12 Feb 2008; Markus Dittrich <markusle@gentoo.org> refbase-0.8.0.ebuild,
  +refbase-0.9.0.ebuild:
  Version bump and added check for php USE flags (see bug #151857).

  05 Feb 2008; Benedikt Böhm <hollow@gentoo.org> refbase-0.8.0.ebuild:
  merge from webapps overlay wrt #208584

  02 Feb 2008; Benedikt Böhm <hollow@gentoo.org> refbase-0.8.0.ebuild:
  use depend.apache eclass wrt #208033. Do not depend on mysql in web
  apps.

  29 Jul 2007; Christian Heim <phreak@gentoo.org> refbase-0.8.0.ebuild:
  Fixing the DEPEND/RDEPEND for the move of net-www/apache to
  www-servers/apache (#78622).

  23 Nov 2006; Francesco Riosa <vivo@gentoo.org> refbase-0.8.0.ebuild:
  dev-db/mysql => virtual/mysql

  17 Oct 2006; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  files/postinstall-en.txt:
  See INSTALL.gz, not INSTALL. Also a note to change the version number in
  files/postinstall-en.txt on bumps.

